      },
      "writtenOn": "2016-04-21T19:05:37Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "These StackSize/MaximumStackSize arguments down here were going to answer my question about the stack from above, but they’re 0. Does that mean “default?”",
      "revId": "0f544b3e831c2d4d922a8fc70f6d60534ed83288",
